        "subject": "LU-10472 osd-ldiskfs: add T10PI support for page cache",
        "message": "LU-10472 osd-ldiskfs: add T10PI support for page cache\n\nWhen OST recieves bulk write RPC, the T10PI checksum of the page will\nbe calculated. When submiting the BIO to disk, the T10PI checksums of\nthe BIO will be verified with the checksums of the pages.\n\nSigned-off-by: Li Xi <lixi@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: I3b21c20d945929a51d51663151bd236961d6d951\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
